<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> Pictures of a mercury arc rectifier in operation can be seen here: <a href="http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/b/belsize_park_deep_shelter/index14.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/b/belsize_park_deep_shelter/index14.shtml" rel="nofollow">Belsize Park deep shelter rectifier 1</a>, <a href="http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/b/belsize_park_deep_shelter/index13.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/b/belsize_park_deep_shelter/index13.shtml" rel="nofollow">Belsize Park deep shelter rectifier 2</a></li>
