<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> <a href="https://inlportal.inl.gov/portal/server.pt?open=514&amp;objID=1269&amp;mode=2&amp;featurestory=DA_101047" class="external text" title="https://inlportal.inl.gov/portal/server.pt?open=514&amp;objID=1269&amp;mode=2&amp;featurestory=DA_101047" rel="nofollow"><i>Harvesting the sun's energy with antennas</i></a> (2007). Idaho National Laboratory. Accessed on 3 October 2008.</li>
</ol>


